name: weblap
description: * Clone the repository * Install dart [sass](https://sass-lang.com/dart-sass "sass") * Add dart sass to path: <https://stackoverflow.com/questions/51571814/how-to-install-dart-sass> * If you are using vscode install the blade runner extension to auto compile sass into css. Or use the command `sass --watch styles.scss styles.css` * Run the server with `python manage.py runserver`
